high_descs: Turn around to go towards the tub then to the left near the plungers and to the right facing the edge of the tub near the wall.
Pick up the purple rag that is sitting in the tub.
Turn to your right then right again to walk away from the tub, then make a right so you are facing the sink near the toilet.
Put the purple rag in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and take the rag back out.
Turn back around and go back towards the tub. Make a left at the tub and turn around to face the toilet.
Place the rag on top of the toilet next to the spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Taking a dirty rag and cleaning it off to put away.

high_descs: turn around ,go toward the bath tub
pick up the dirty rag out of the tub
turn around go toward the sink
put the rag in the sink, turn on the water to clean the rag after that turn the water off then pick up the rag
turn around, go toward the  bath tub and turn right to go to the toilet
put the rag on top of the toilet tank next to the cleaner
Turn around and walk to the tub and then turn left walk to the wall then turn right to look at the tub again.
Pick up the purple wash cloth.
Walk around the toilet so you are standing in front of the sink facing it.
Clean the wash cloth in the sink and pick it back up.
Walk back to where you got the washcloth but look the opposite way so you are looking at the green towel on a ring across the room.
Put the clean washcloth on the back of the toilet to the left of the green spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean washcloth on the back of the toilet.
